The article is a letter from President Joseph R. Biden Jr. to the Chairman (or Chairwoman) regarding the annual report on the legal and policy frameworks guiding the United States' use of military force and related national security operations. The letter is in compliance with section 1264 of the National Defense Authorization Act for fiscal year 2018. President Biden includes an unclassified notice and a classified annex with the letter. The letter is dated March 3, 2021.